{"tid":1310452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請認清目標］我覺得大家開始團結返","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:43:00.000Z","uid":262084,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9281c9a530cb3603dcdd55e7640229ff11cf4b77","tid":1310452,"uid":262084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:21:44.000Z","msg":"市區普遍對連濃牆沒想像中大反感，除了個別藍絲外，但因為早排打人事件也不敢太昌闕了<br />\n<br />\n就算有廢老搞事都係圍佢既市民多，有D中年人都持觀望態度起碼唔反對<br />\n<br />\n做得好各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續加油！<br />\n<br />\n下一步我覺得可以真搞多D後生仔市區活動，例如齊齊清潔街道日 or 去探獨居老人，做多D社區工作去爭取佢地既認同，唔好吓吓人地唔同意見就屌人廢老，其實有D係可以做frd轉化的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家積極D考慮吓做實事反擊吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目標係出年立法會選舉！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5a1ce362623411dd1c5b73ce6f7408013617c9bc","tid":1310452,"uid":176112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該入去簽一簽, 記得 confirm埋 Email </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqPuJua8aDO26H7yvH2Ijw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqPuJua8aDO26H7yvH2Ijw&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=e401a10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR1smpzMZRa1dPl0VFsxGc6IDORtJlyl2GRBLvqPuJua8aDO26H7yvH2Ijw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJmPogL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2